1
00:00:09,967 --> 00:00:13,333
<i>Noah, I won't get tired
of thanking you.</i>

2
00:00:13,467 --> 00:00:17,333
<i>Because you're always
there for us.</i>

3
00:00:17,467 --> 00:00:18,333
<i> Hello, Jeff?</i>

4
00:00:18,467 --> 00:00:20,033
<i> What's your mom doing?</i>

5
00:00:20,167 --> 00:00:21,467
<i> Dad, Mom went out.</i>

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,133
<i> Is she with Noah?</i>

7
00:00:23,267 --> 00:00:26,600
<i> No, Auntie Paz called earlier.</i>

8
00:00:26,733 --> 00:00:30,533
<i>Coleen, Andrea, and I will go
to Jessica's grave.</i>

9
00:00:30,967 --> 00:00:32,033
<i> Dad!</i>

10
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:35,867
<i>I'm always hoping
and praying that someday,</i>

11
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:38,133
<i>our family will be whole again.</i>

12
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:40,500
<i> I miss you so much, kids.</i>

13
00:00:41,267 --> 00:00:42,533
<i> I love you with all my heart.</i>

14
00:00:46,733 --> 00:00:50,000
Dear, rest in peace, okay?

15
00:00:51,333 --> 00:00:52,367
Always remember that...

16
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:56,333
