20
00:01:29,100 --> 00:01:33,867
And he's putting Hazel
in her place properly.

21
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,267
Amazing.

22
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:39,067
As for me, I'm just happy
we got to be with Dad again.

23
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:42,100
We got to talk to him
and hug him.

24
00:01:43,633 --> 00:01:47,733
I hope there's a lot more
to come.

25
00:01:49,033 --> 00:01:52,733
But honestly, I'm losing it.

26
00:01:52,867 --> 00:01:55,400
Ma'am Felma really
can't remember

27
00:01:55,533 --> 00:01:57,500
