<i> Dad...</i>

57
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,633
<i> Please forgive me.</i>

58
00:03:50,767 --> 00:03:52,400
<i> Mom and me.</i>

59
00:03:52,533 --> 00:03:54,200
<i> Please forgive us, Dad.</i>

60
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,233
