84
00:05:01,133 --> 00:05:03,033
Tell me the truth, Hazel!
Confess!

85
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,100
Confess!

86
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,867
Let go of me!
Let go!

87
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,233
No.

88
00:05:14,367 --> 00:05:16,500
Not until you tell me
your secret with Jessica.

89
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,833
<i>Your dad and I got married
in February.</i>

90
00:05:20,933 --> 00:05:23,100
