even hide from you?

99
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:51,867
Isn't it you two who kept
secrets from me back then?

100
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:53,800
Come on, Manuel?

101
00:05:53,933 --> 00:05:55,700
you're getting mad at me
because of your dream?

102
00:05:55,833 --> 00:05:57,200
