Holy Mary, Mother of God,
pray for us sinners,

107
00:06:18,533 --> 00:06:20,567
now and at the hour
of our death. Amen.

108
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,633
Hail Mary, full of grace,

109
00:06:21,767 --> 00:06:23,100
the Lord is with you.

110
00:06:24,033 --> 00:06:25,167
Blessed are you amongst women,

111
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:28,033
and blessed is the fruit
of your womb, Jesus.

112
00:06:28,167 --> 00:06:30,367
Holy Mary, Mother of God,
pray for us sinners,

113
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:32,333
now and at the hour
