Hail Mary,
full of grace...

115
00:06:34,967 --> 00:06:35,833
Dad.

116
00:06:35,967 --> 00:06:36,833
<i> Hello, Jeff.</i>

117
00:06:36,967 --> 00:06:38,833
I need a favor.

118
00:06:39,633 --> 00:06:41,133
But don't tell your siblings,

119
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:42,433
<i> especially your mother.</i>

120
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,867
Hail Mary, full of grace...

121
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,033
All right.

122
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,667
Yes, thank you so much, son.

123
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,500
<i> You're welcome, Dad.</i>

124
00:06:53,633 --> 00:06:55,433
<i> Okay, I'll look for it.</i>

125
00:06:55,567 --> 00:06:56,500
All right, then.

126
00:06:58,900 --> 00:06:59,833
Hazel.

127
00:06:59,967 --> 00:07:01,067
How long have you had this?

128
00:07:02,633 --> 00:07:03,700
All this time,
you've been talking

129
00:07:03,833 --> 00:07:05,067
