You're such a liar.

134
00:07:12,567 --> 00:07:14,967
You're using this to talk
to your mistress!

135
00:07:15,133 --> 00:07:16,700
- Hazel, give it!
- No.

136
00:07:16,833 --> 00:07:18,667
Give it to me!

137
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,867
Hazel! Hazel, give it here!

138
