149
00:07:56,867 --> 00:07:59,267
Manuel, what are you doing? huh?

150
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,633
What are you doing? Manuel?
What's that?

151
00:08:01,767 --> 00:08:03,167
If you're just cutting off
my communication

152
