Didang!

157
00:08:30,300 --> 00:08:31,967
You brought a man in here?

158
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:34,800
Oh! No, Ma'am, no.

159
00:08:34,933 --> 00:08:37,867
I was just talking
to my new friend.

160
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,767
Then he sent me
a picture like this.

161
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:43,433
Hey! What the...

162
00:08:43,567 --> 00:08:46,767
And you're gonna send him
a naked photo, too?

163
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:49,667
Oh, Didang, don't do that.

164
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,600
He might blackmail you.

165
00:08:51,733 --> 00:08:56,100
Then he'll spread it online
if you don't pay.

166
00:08:56,267 --> 00:08:59,067
Of course, Ma'am,
I wouldn't do that.

167
00:09:00,333 --> 00:09:01,500
Oh?

168
00:09:02,067 --> 00:09:05,400
Ma'am, you really love me.

169
00:09:05,533 --> 00:09:07,367
- You're worried about me.
- Of course I am.

170
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:08,600
Of course.

171
