182
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:37,900
You never know, Ma'am.

183
00:09:38,033 --> 00:09:40,500
Some people secretly had...

184
00:09:41,533 --> 00:09:43,100
No, wait,
let me redo that, Ma'am.

185
00:09:43,233 --> 00:09:45,733
Some witches, evil people,

186
00:09:45,867 --> 00:09:48,033
are openly angry at us, right?

187
00:09:48,167 --> 00:09:50,900
Let's just call her Hazel.

188
00:09:51,467 --> 00:09:53,800
Ma'am, do you want to get
a cleansing?

189
00:09:53,933 --> 00:09:55,733
I know someone,
she's really good.

190
00:09:55,867 --> 00:09:56,800
Yes, Ma'am.

191
00:09:56,933 --> 00:09:59,433
Didang, you're imagining things.

192
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:02,933
You know what I need?

193
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:04,433
A long sleep.

194
00:10:14,133 --> 00:10:16,800
No, Hazel,
I'm serious.

195
00:10:16,933 --> 00:10:19,133
You know how important
my kids are to me.

196
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,767
That's why I was forced
to marry you back then.

197
00:10:22,900 --> 00:10:23,967
Because we were going
to have a child.

198
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:26,167
Not because I loved you.

199
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:28,333
You always know how to cut deep.

200
00:10:30,267 --> 00:10:31,867
That hurts, Manuel.

201
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:33,967
Why? It's the truth.

202
00:10:36,467 --> 00:10:38,500
What? Are we going
to pretend now?

203
00:10:38,633 --> 00:10:40,533
We've already shown
our true colors.

204
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:45,633
Hazel, I already chose you,
I left Felma again for you!

205
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:48,867
But if you're going to take me
away from my kids, then fine,

206
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,867
